        "desc": "<p>從世界之外漂流而來的旅行者，被神帶走血親，自此踏上尋找七神之路。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/16/7998136/04f769b0b1671b5ffbbafefd7286b4b2_1946573755897168794.png",
