        "name": "安",
        "desc": "<p>由「瑪麗安」的意識創造的純水精靈。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/04/157749474/7a4364ee7ecfbf1eb2b78fbf7b6607ed_3554222362796444925.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4520,
        "name": "卡特皮拉",
        "desc": "<p>水仙十字結社的一名成員，被授予「幻光蝶蛾之蛹」的稱號。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/157749474/be516a2c9005727dcfd1fe45662a826d_3682068746055334164.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4255,
        "name": "「瑪麗安」",
        "desc": "<p>生活在安眠處的純水精靈。<span class=\"wk-shady\">她是由莉利絲和瑪麗安·吉約丹融合而成的混合意識純水精靈。</span></p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/157749474/7ac751c3fd3892141d972392696a414b_6216911789115688466.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
