        "name": "瑪麗安·吉約丹",
        "desc": "<p>埃馬紐艾爾·吉約丹的養女，與哥哥阿蘭在水仙十字院長大。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/157749474/7f04e9d0b83ab550cc91ddf708008a7d_3962428389587493975.png",
